			<td align="left" valign="middle" valign="top"><br>
				<font face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" size="2" color=white><blockquote>
1.</b>	Slay Sir Edwin Motte (33rd level Paladin) at the Inn at the Docks in East Freeport, bring his head to Kazen Facae, at location 340 –1600 in Nektulos Forest<br>&nbsp;<br>
2.</b>	Ask Kazen 'What about a symbol of the apprentice?', receive symbol.<br>&nbsp;<br>
3.</b>	Take the symbol to Venenzi Oberzendi, at -1000 -700.  in Nektulos Fores.<br>&nbsp;<br>
4.</b>	Ask her, “What Task” and she will ask for a Flowing Black Robe.  Give Venenzi Oberzendi a Flowing Black Robe (dropped by Najena in Najena), receive Twisted Symbol of the Apprentice and Moss<br>&nbsp;<br>
5.</b>	Go to Lake Rathe and give Emkel, Fazen’s (–1500, 200) Apprentice the Twisted Symbol of the Apprentice and Moss.  Receive Symbol of the Serpent.<br>&nbsp;<br>
6.</b>	Take Symbol of the Serpent to Ssessthrass, a named Iksar in the Swamp of No Hope. He is at location 3800, 1600, in a house in the pass to go to Field of Bone. He will give you Scaled Symbol of the Serpent.  Get Symbol back.<br>&nbsp;<br>
7.</b>	Head to Chardok and kill the Royal Sarnak Herbalist (center spawn in the hut near the offduty sarnak quarters) and loot Mansini Herb.<br>&nbsp;<br>
8.</b>	Give Mansini Herb and Scaled Symbol of the Serpent to Ssessthrass and receive Refined Mansini Herb.<br>&nbsp;<br>
9.</b>	Now go back to Emkel and give him the Refined Manisi Herb. You will receive a Symbol of Testing.<br>&nbsp;<br>
10.</b>	Get a good kill group together and give the Symbol of Testing to Kazen. Immediately after, three mobs will spawn close by to the East of Emkel on a little inlet.  The three mobs are Bone Golem, Failed Apprentice, and Tormented Spirit. The Bone Golem and the Tormented Spirit were both level 55 and the Failed Apprentice was blue to a 53. The three mobs spawn one after another right after the previous one dies (in the order listed above). The last MOB the Tormented Spirit drops the Symbol of Insanity.<br>&nbsp;<br>
11.</b>	Go to Timmorous Deep and give the Symbol of Insanity to Drendico Metalbones, on the hills near the Docks from Overthere around 6480, 3830.  Receive his journal and asks for   The Eye of Innoruuk, Blood of Cazic-Thule, and Cloak of Spiroc Feathers.<br>&nbsp;<br>
12.</b>	Get Eye of Innoruuk drops from mini-bosses in old Hate and Innoruuk.<br>&nbsp;<br>
13.</b>	Get Slime Blood of Cazic Thule, drops off Terror and Cazic Thule.<br>&nbsp;<br>
14.</b>	Get Cape of Spiroc Feathers (note this is only one of many ways to do this)<br>&nbsp;<br>
<blockquote>
a.</b>	Bind yourself and a Wizard/Druid at docks in NRo. (Prep)<br>&nbsp;<br>
b.</b>	Gate raid up to PoA.<br>&nbsp;<br>
c.</b>	Buy Key of Veshan from Key Master. This is the key to the Quest Den.<br>&nbsp;<br>
d.</b>	Give the Princess the 1pp or 10gp before moving to island 2. This spawns Gkzallk on Grogalosk Island. Note, for every 1pp/10gp given by each player, will spawn a Gkzallk on Grog Island.<br>&nbsp;<br>
e.</b>	Kill Azerak's until a Silver disc drops off Isle 2, trash MOB’s. (Azarack Island)<br>&nbsp;<br>
f.</b>	Kill Gorgalask's, and Spirited Harpies until a Spiroc feathers (one item, named plural) drop, off trash MOB’s. (Grogalosk Island)<br>&nbsp;<br>
g.</b>	Kill Keeper of Souls for Black Silk Cape (*Isle 4, see farming below - Pegasus Isle).<br>&nbsp;<br>
h.</b>	Once you have all cloak quest parts, get killed on Isle 4 (Pegasus Island) (not duel, death). ** Note 2<br>&nbsp;<br>
i.</b>	Rez back and loot everything but ONE item, leaving corpse there. Gate with a Wiz back to Island 1.<br>&nbsp;<br>
j.</b>	Buy Key to Quest Isle and finish Cloak quest (Quest Isle). Use Key of Veshan on other ring on Island 1. Go to Drakis Bloodcaster ask him "Who is Jzil". Give book he gives you right back to him. This spawns Jzil. Give Jzil Black Silk Cape, Silver Disc, Sporic feathers (only one feather), receive Cape.<br>&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>
**Keeper is farmed by killing ONE Pegasus or Griffon, plus all subsequent sub-spawns. This causes Nottap Ekim to spawn on island 4. When he de-spawns the Keeper should spawn in 80 minutes. Assuming you only killed the ONE mob so far and Keeper is now up, kill ONLY the Keeper, wait for Sirran to de-spawn. Restart cycle again kill another mob from island 4, this causes the Keeper cycle to restart.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>
** First option for final step is to summon corpse onto Island 1, create a key corpse and then use keys and invisibility to get to Gkzallk.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>
** Second Option is to with your back to Gargolak Island on Djarn Isle, duel someone with a Chetari Ward staff and hope for a Grav Flux proc to send you to Gargolak Isle.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>
** Third Option for the final step is just port up to Djarn isle (sword key), aim at the Gargolak Island, back off into the sawmill, look up and run. As soon as you see the top doorway of sawmill somehow radically quit out of EQ (unplug connection, hit your Windows Key, power off your system). When you will log back from ld you will be in the right island. Author has not tested this way, but I hear it works.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>
</blockquote>
15.</b>	Gate to NRo with Wizard/Druid and do turn in of Cloak, Eye, Blood and Journal to Drendico – receive a Prepared Reagent Box.<br>&nbsp;<br>
16.</b>	Gate to SK (from Wizard/Druid, run to LR and take Box to Kazen (Lake Rathe) Get Tome Of Instruction. Bind yourself to Lake Rathe.Get Rez back to corpse on Pegasus Island. Wait for rez effects to fade, get SOW, cast Harmshield or QvoX and jump/run off finger SW edge of Pegasus Island that overlaps Gorgalask Island. Give Gkzzallk Tome of Instruction and get Gkzallk In A Box. (can switch with death on Island 4, rez to Island 4 and then SOW, Harm Shield, run/jump to Island 3 for turn in).<br>&nbsp;<br>
17.</b>	Self Gate to LR, turn in Gkzallk In a Box to Kazen get Duck.<br>&nbsp;<br>
